BASF’s Voscherau Against Quota for Women, FT Deutschland Says

-- B y   R i c h a r d   W e i s s
-- 
2011-04-26T20:30:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/basf-s-voscherau-against-quota-for-women-ft-deutschland-says.html
Eggert Voscherau, chairman of the
supervisory board of  BASF SE (BAS)  and head of  Germany ’s chemical
employers association, opposes a quota for women managers as it
wouldn’t increase the number of female candidates available for
higher management positions,  Financial Times Deutschland  said in
a news release previewing tomorrow’s edition.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Richard Weiss in  Frankfurt  at 
 rweiss5@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at   bkammel@bloomberg.net . 